"{\"uid\": \"npr.org-2024-08-13-g-s1-16588-british-olympic-diver-tom-daley-retirement\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By  Ayana Archie  Diver Tom Daley of Team GB arrives back in the United Kingdom at St. Pancras International Station on Monday in London.Leon Neal/Getty Imageshide caption  British Olympic diver Tom Daley, who has won five medals and went viral in the Paris games for his sideline knitting, is retiring.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_in_the_Junior_Eurovision_Song_Contest_2021\", \"score\": 0.6852260982767685, \"rank\": 0.45937216327486274, \"text\": \"Ayana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_in_the_Junior_Eurovision_Song_Contest_2021\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_in_the_Junior_Eurovision_Song_Contest_2021\"}, {\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archie_Andrews\", \"score\": 0.7663325535475408, \"rank\": 0.30203686226447296, \"text\": \"Archie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archie_Andrews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archie_Andrews\"}, {\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.12480536570858e-35, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999991346007043, \"rank\": 6.235296190985472e-07, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9299491180960963, \"rank\": 0.07452945944785001, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.12480536570858e-35, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999815991034, \"rank\": 1.8400967423644637e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive,\\\"he told Voguein an interview published Monday.\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the right time to call it a day.\\\"\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley, 30, first began his Olympic career at age 14 in the 2008 Beijing Games.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has since won three bronze medals, one gold medal and most recently, a silver in the men's 10-meter synchronized platform event at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He went on a two-year hiatus from the sport following the Tokyo Games, and has overcome several hurdles over the course of his career, including breaking a hand, tearing a tricep, hitting his head on the platform and getting a case of the \\\"twisties,\\\" he told British Vogue.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1572752180574286e-23, \"text\": \"British Vogue\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He lent his expertise as a pundit during the Paris Games, has planned to start his own underwear and swimwear line and has signed up for a sewing class at the Fashion Institute of Design and Merchandising (FIDM) in Los Angeles, adding to hisrepertoire of knitting and crocheting.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999957701675, \"rank\": 4.167946733083444e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you, diving over and out,\\\" he said on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.608039606563169e-15, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sponsor Message  Become an NPR sponsor\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"score\": 0.9999994728890694, \"rank\": 5.215770241761341e-07, \"text\": \"NPR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NPR\"}]}]}"